short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: With just a single mouse click each, you can identify any apparel on-screen, bookmark to you personal e-wardrobe, and check out.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Whenever you come across any apparel that you like, just tap the FITTD icon on the right corner of your screen. Then, when you open the FITTD extension, just tap "Find Similar Items". Our AI does the magic for you and finds similar fits.

You can save items by double tapping the heart button, and find them in the "My Wardrobe" tab. Just tap on any item to see more information.
